column3: It was nice to think about the zones that are possible, but to be very honest im not entirely sure that i did it correctly. i tried to make the largest zones possible but maybe because the building was two layer and all spaces were more or less connected it led to only two zones most of the time.

column3: Yes i think so, because i think AI wouldve done a better job at understanding the zoning and would not have made the error of not considering stiffness.

column4: but that could be because i did not entirely understand the concept. with a little bit more training i think i could have done a similar job as AI or even a bit better in the sense that i could have made less mistakes.
